","Gen."],"3:16"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/4.22"},"Moses 4:22"],"; )"],["li","when Rachel saw that she bare Jacob no",["i","children"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/gen/30.1"},["span.padWord","Gen."],"30:1"],";"],["li","visiting the iniquity of the fathers upon the",["i","children"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/20.5"},"Ex. 20:5"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/34.7"},["span.padWord","Ex."],"34:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/num/14.18"},"Num. 14:18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/5.9"},"Deut. 5:9"],"; )"],["li","that they may teach their",["i","children"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/4.10"},"Deut. 4:10"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/11.19-21"},["span.padWord","Deut."],"11:19–21"],"; )"],["li","shalt teach them diligently unto thy",["i","children"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/6.7"},["span.padWord","Deut."],"6:7"],";"],["li","Ye are the",["i","children"],"of the Lord:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/14.1"},["span.padWord","Deut."],"14:1"],";"],["li","fathers shall not be put to death for the",["i","children"],", neither shall the",["i","children"],"be:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/24.16"},["span.padWord","Deut."],"24:16"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/14.6"},"2 Kgs. 14:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-chr/25.4"},"2 Chr. 25:4"],"; )"],["li","when your",["i","children"],"ask their fathers:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/4.6"},"Josh. 4:6"],";"],["li","ye shall let your",["i","children"],"know:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/4.22"},["span.padWord","Josh."],"4:22"],";"],["li","two she bears … tare forty and two",["i","children"],"of them:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/2.24"},"2 Kgs. 2:24"],";"],["li","Out of the mouth of",["i","babes"],"… hast thou ordained strength:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/8.2"},"Ps. 8:2"],";"],["li","you are",["i","children"],"of the most High:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/82.6"},["span.padWord","Ps."],"82:6"],";"],["li","be a joyful mother of",["i","children"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/113.9"},["span.padWord","Ps."],"113:9"],";"],["li",["i","children"],"are an heritage of the Lord:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/127.3"},["span.padWord","Ps."],"127:3"],";"],["li","Happy is the man that hath his quiver",["i","full"],"of them:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/127.5"},["span.padWord","Ps."],"127:5"],";"],["li","Hear, ye",["i","children"],", the instruction of a father:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/4.1"},"Prov. 4:1"],";"],["li","glory of",["i","children"],"are their fathers:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/17.6"},["span.padWord","Prov."],"17:6"],";"],["li","Her",["i","children"],"arise up, and call her blessed:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/31.28"},["span.padWord","Prov."],"31:28"],";"],["li",["i","children"],"that are corrupters:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/1.4"},"Isa. 1:4"],";"],["li","I will give",["i","children"],"to be their princes:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/3.4"},["span.padWord","Isa."],"3:4"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.4"},"2 Ne. 13:4"],"; )"],["li","As for my people,",["i","children"],"are their oppressors:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/3.12"},["span.padWord","Isa."],"3:12"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/13.12"},"2 Ne. 13:12"],"; )"],["li","lying",["i","children"],",",["i","children"],"that will not hear the law:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/30.9"},["span.padWord","Isa."],"30:9"],";"],["li","more are the",["i","children"],"of the desolate:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/54.1"},["span.padWord","Isa."],"54:1"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/4.27"},"Gal. 4:27"],"; )"],["li","all thy",["i","children"],"shall be taught of the Lord:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/54.13"},["span.padWord","Isa."],"54:13"],";"],["li","they are my people,",["i","children"],"that will not lie:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/63.8"},["span.padWord","Isa."],"63:8"],";"],["li","as Zion travailed, she brought forth her",["i","children"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/66.8"},["span.padWord","Isa."],"66:8"],";"],["li","the",["i","children’s"],"teeth are set on edge:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/31.29"},"Jer. 31:29"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/18.2"},"Ezek. 18:2"],"; )"],["li",["i","Children"],"in whom was no blemish:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/dan/1.4"},"Dan. 1:4"],";"],["li","turn … the heart of the",["i","children"],"to their fathers:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/mal/4.6"},"Mal. 4:6"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/1.17"},"Luke 1:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/2"},"D&C 2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/98.16"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"98:16"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.39"},"JS—H 1:39"],"; )"]]],["div",{"id":"f3","uri":"/scriptures/tg/children.f3","order":".000.1471"},["ul.index",["li","slew all the",["i","children"],"that were in Bethlehem:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.16"},"Matt. 2:16"],";"],["li","Rachel weeping for her",["i","children"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/2.18"},["span.padWord","Matt."],"2:18"],";"],["li","stones to raise up",["i","children"],"unto Abraham:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/3.9"},["span.padWord","Matt."],"3:9"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/3.8"},"Luke 3:8"],"; )"],["li","peacemakers … shall be called the",["i","children"],"of God:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/5.9"},["span.padWord","Matt."],"5:9"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/12.9"},"3 Ne. 12:9"],"; )"],["li","That ye may be the",["i","children"],"of your Father:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/5.45"},["span.padWord","Matt."],"5:45"],";"],["li","to give good gifts unto your",["i","children"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/7.11"},["span.padWord","Matt."],"7:11"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/11.13"},"Luke 11:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/14.11"},"3 Ne. 14:11"],"; )"],["li",["i","children"],"of the kingdom shall be cast out:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/8.12"},["span.padWord","Matt."],"8:12"],";"],["li",["i","children"],"of the bridechamber:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/9.15"},["span.padWord","Matt."],"9:15"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/2.19"},"Mark 2:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/5.34"},"Luke 5:34"],"; )"],["li",["i","children"],"shall rise up against their parents:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/10.21"},["span.padWord","Matt."],"10:21"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/13.12"},"Mark 13:12"],"; )"],["li","wisdom is justified of her",["i","children"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/11.19"},["span.padWord","Matt."],"11:19"],";"],["li","Except ye … become as little",["i","children"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/18.3"},["span.padWord","Matt."],"18:3"],";"],["li","despise not one of these",["i","little ones"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/18.10"},["span.padWord","Matt."],"18:10"],";"],["li","not the will of your Father … that one of these",["i","little ones"],"should perish:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/18.14"},["span.padWord","Matt."],"18:14"],";"],["li","Suffer little",["i","children"],", and forbid them not:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/19.14"},["span.padWord","Matt."],"19:14"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/10.14"},"Mark 10:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/18.16"},"Luke 18:16"],"; )"],["li","If a man die, having no",["i","children"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/22.24"},["span.padWord","Matt."],"22:24"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/25.5"},"Deut. 25:5"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/12.19"},"Mark 12:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.28"},"Luke 20:28"],"; )"],["li","shall receive one of such",["i","children"],"in my name:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/9.37"},"Mark 9:37"],";"],["li","ye shall be the",["i","children"],"of the Highest:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/6.35"},"Luke 6:35"],";"],["li",["i","children"],"of God, being the",["i","children"],"of the resurrection:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/20.36"},["span.padWord","Luke"],"20:36"],";"],["li","If ye were Abraham’s",["i","children"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/8.39"},"John 8:39"],";"],["li","he should gather together in one the",["i","children"],"of God:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/11.52"},["span.padWord","John"],"11:52"],";"],["li","Little",["i","children"],", yet a little while I am with you:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/13.33"},["span.padWord","John"],"13:33"],";"],["li","beareth witness with our spirit, that we are the",["i","children"],"of God:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/8.16"},"Rom. 8:16"],";"],["li",["i","children"],"of the promise are counted for the seed:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/9.8"},["span.padWord","Rom."],"9:8"],";"],["li","shall they be called the",["i","children"],"of the living God:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/rom/9.26"},["span.padWord","Rom."],"9:26"],";"],["li","else were your",["i","children"],"unclean:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/7.14"},"1 Cor. 7:14"],";"],["li","be not",["i","children"],"in understanding: howbeit in malice be ye",["i","children"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/14.20"},["span.padWord","1 Cor."],"14:20"],";"],["li","they which are of faith, the same are the",["i","children"],"of Abraham:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.7"},"Gal. 3:7"],";"],["li","ye are all the",["i","children"],"of God by faith in Christ:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/3.26"},["span.padWord","Gal."],"3:26"],";"],["li","Now we, brethren, as Isaac was, are the",["i","children"],"of promise:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/gal/4.28"},["span.padWord","Gal."],"4:28"],";"],["li","be no more",["i","children"],", tossed to and fro:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/4.14"},"Eph. 4:14"],";"],["li","walk as",["i","children"],"of light:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/5.8"},["span.padWord","Eph."],"5:8"],";"],["li",["i","Children"],", obey your parents in the Lord:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/eph/6.1"},["span.padWord","Eph."],"6:1"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/col/3.20"},"Col. 3:20"],"; )"],["li","charged every one of you, as a father doth his",["i","children"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-thes/2.11"},"1 Thes. 2:11"],";"],["li","ruleth well his own house, having his",["i","children"],"in subjection with all gravity:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-tim/3.4"},"1 Tim. 3:4"],";"],["li",["i","children"],"… learn first to shew piety at home:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-tim/5.4"},["span.padWord","1 Tim."],"5:4"],";"],["li","teach the young women … to love their",["i","children"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/titus/2.4"},"Titus 2:4"],";"],["li","As obedient",["i","children"],", not fashioning yourselves:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-pet/1.14"},"1 Pet. 1:14"],";"],["li","I write unto you, little",["i","children"],", because your sins are forgiven:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-jn/2.12"},"1 Jn. 2:12"],";"],["li","In this the",["i","children"],"of God are manifest, and the",["i","children"],"of the devil:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-jn/3.10"},["span.padWord","1 Jn."],"3:10"],";"],["li","we love the",["i","children"],"of God, when we love God:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-jn/5.2"},["span.padWord","1 Jn."],"5:2"],";"],["li","joy than to hear that my",["i","children"],"walk in truth:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/3-jn/1.4"},"3 Jn. 1:4"],";"]]],["div",{"id":"f4","uri":"/scriptures/tg/children.f4","order":".000.1472"},["ul.index",["li","he hath created his",["i","children"],"that they should possess it:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/17.36"},"1 Ne. 17:36"],";"],["li","they would have had no",["i","children"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/2.23"},"2 Ne. 2:23"],";"],["li","learning and … profit of my",["i","children"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/4.15"},["span.padWord","2 Ne."],"4:15"],";"],["li","we write … that our",["i","children"],"may know:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/25.26"},["span.padWord","2 Ne."],"25:26"],";"],["li","lost the confidence of your",["i","children"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/2.35"},"Jacob 2:35"],";"],["li","remember your",["i","children"],", how that ye have grieved their hearts:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/jacob/3.10"},["span.padWord","Jacob"],"3:10"],";"],["li","taught them to his",["i","children"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/1.4"},"Mosiah 1:4"],";"],["li","if it were possible that little",["i","children"],"could sin:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/mosiah/3.16"},["span.padWord","Mosiah"],"3:16"],";"],["li","not suffer your",["i","children"],"that they go hungry:",["a.scriptureR